-
UBRELVY is a prescription medicine used to treat migraine attacks in adults. Itâs not for migraine prevention. Talk to your healthcare provider about UBRELVY and whether itâs right for you. There are risks with this product. Do not take with strong CYP3A4 inhibitors. Few people had side effects. The most common were nausea (2-4%) and tiredness (2-3%). In clinical studies, most people had pain relief and some had pain freedom within 2 hours.
